subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. Western Atlantic: Panama and Brazil ( Ceará , Sergipe , Bahia , Rio de Janeiro , São Paulo ) ( Rhyne & Lin 2006 ;
Barros-Alves et al. 2015
;
Pachelle et al. 2016
) ( Fig. 16 ).

Ecology . Typically on hard and mixed bottoms, such as rocky reefs and shallow fossilised reef terraces with abundance of small caves and other shelters, depth range: 1–25 m ( Rhyne & Lin 2006 ;
Barros-Alves et al. 2015
).
